//   single check: (density-0x40) <= 0x1E AND bit set in 0x55000055 (plus density==0)
// PATCHED:   {0x00, 0x40, 0x42, 0x44, 0x46, 0x58, 0x5A, 0x5C, 0x5E, 0x60}
//   branch density<=0x58: (density-0x40) <= 0x18 AND bit set in 0x1000055 (plus density==0)
//   branch density>0x58: ((density-0x5A) & 0xF9)==0 or density==0x60  -> accepts 0x5A,0x5C,0x5E,0x60
// Difference: 0x60 added; nothing removed.
